<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śakavaruṣaṁbulu 13<unclear>0</unclear>1 gunēṁṭi mārggaśira vimala da
<lb n="2" break="no"/>śamiyu Ādivāramunāṁḍu kaḷiṁggamajikaṁssanārayaṇa
<lb n="3"/>viśvanātajīyana tanaku Abhīṣṭārttasiddigānu śrīnarasiṁhya
<lb n="4" break="no"/>nātuniki nityamunnu tirumāla sātiṁppanu śrīkāryyamuna I<unclear>li</unclear>
<lb n="5"/>Aluṁḍu cuḍamaṇi [A]gnapūṁḍiAṁdu jalakṣētramu puṭṭaṁ
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ḍu peṭṭenu I kṣētrāna danyamu bhujiṁcci I cūḍamaṇi A
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ddiṣṭānamaṁdu Anāvāla Anama nityamunu tirumāla Ācaṁ
<lb n="8" break="no"/>drārtthasthaIgānu peṭaṁgalāṁḍu I darmu śrīvaiṣṇava ra
<lb n="9" break="no"/>kṣa <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śatṛnāpi kritō dharmaḥ palanī<unclear>yō</unclear> manīśi<unclear>biḥ</unclear> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śatṛrēvā
<lb n="10" break="no"/>hi(ḥ) satṛsyāddharmaśatṛrnna kasyacittu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrī śrī śrī visvana
<lb n="11" break="no"/>thajīyyana bhāryya śrī <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> dēvi tanaku Iṣṭartthasiddiṁgā
<lb n="12" break="no"/>nu śrībaṁḍāramaṁdu padmanidhi maḍalu 4 peṭṭi kuṁcapra
<lb n="13" break="no"/>sa<unclear>da</unclear>mu vṛttigāṁ baḍaci nityamu ṟepuṁ caṁdanalāgi Apu<supplied reason="omitted">ḍu</supplied>
<lb n="14"/>Ālavaṭṭamu paṭṭa śrīkāryya cuḍamaṇikiṁ <unclear>beṭṭe</unclear>nu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
